  "id": "ee4e734848989020289cacd1f461b69a",
  "publisher": "the_boys",
  "about": "The Boys is an American satirical superhero television series developed by Eric Kripke for Amazon Prime Video. Based on the comic book series by Garth Ennis and Darick Robertson, it follows the eponymous team of vigilantes as they combat superpowered individuals, referred to as \"Supes\", who often abuse their powers for personal gain and work for a powerful company, Vought International, that ensures the general public views them as heroes. The series stars Karl Urban, Jack Quaid, Antony Starr, Erin Moriarty, Dominique McElligott, Jessie T. Usher, Chace Crawford, Laz Alonso, Tomer Capone, Karen Fukuhara, Nathan Mitchell, Elisabeth Shue, Colby Minifie, Aya Cash, Claudia Doumit, Jensen Ackles, Cameron Crovetti, Susan Heyward, Valorie Curry, Jeffrey Dean Morgan, and Daveed Diggs.",
